race.comment: PRE EMINENCE (3) returned in good order with a dominant Toowoomba win over this sprint trip and will have come on with that run now in the locker. Gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim and can go back-to-back to start the preparation. PETTICOAT (12) has a handy record over this five-furlong trip with two wins and two placings from six attempts. Handles all going and should be in this for a long way. FIND YOUR OWN (2) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Yet to taste defeat in three starts over this track and trip and is a must for the exotics players. SOUTHERN CHARM (11) is first-up here but has revved up for this with two recent trials and can run a race while fresh. SHE OURS (16) next in line from the favourable draw.
